<br>
2. Chain cast your invuln line - Summon your pet and chain cast (as needed) your re-agentless invuln spells on your pet. Can't recall when you get these spells, but they are spread all over. Very effective once you slow your target and just sit and med up inbetween casts. I still do this from time to time.<br>
<br>
